cc:Work.dc:title: Devil Head
cc:Work.dc:description: I think that user sergSB uploads some great clipart, but it is often monolingual and not so well suited to general use. (With this one, I imagined someone could use this any time they needed to have a devil head... although, I'm not sure when that would be!) So I hope sergSB doesn't mind if I upload more general use remixes of the provided clipart, so that they can be more widely enjoyed :)
